<ab facs="#facs_63_r2l4">vnd <expan>hölcʒ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe in das ambt gen fürt gehörn / <expan>Dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / an <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
